{"tid":1721421,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發｜參院剛啟動「熱線」機制 六小時內無人反對即通過《法案》","createTime":"2019-11-14T15:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T16:16:00.000Z","uid":282979,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ac56cb8cef517a79e5f24d674f843e1a77013142","tid":1721421,"uid":282979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:54:56.000Z","msg":"【🇺🇸突發｜參院剛啟動「熱線」機制 六小時內無人反對即通過《法案》】<br />\n<br />\n剛剛習近平在金磚國家領導人會晤上，提出「止暴制亂是香港當前最緊迫的任務」、恐嚇香港人之際，同一時間，美國國會再度出手。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志駐華盛頓代表敖卓軒收到消息，得悉Mitch McConnell剛剛將《法案》提交參議院審議，並啟動「熱線」（hotline）機制。<br />\n<br />\n在「熱線」機制下，《法案》提交後六小時內（即香港時間星期五凌晨5點前），沒有參議員反對的話，就當作參議院一致通過，法案就會明早交到白宮處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/demosisto/posts/1252853104923509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdemosisto%2Fposts%2F1252853104923509&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc68jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=36d5a532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/demosisto/posts/1252853104923509</a>"},{"pid":"55443eaf60309685d04369af44a7a35b03febfff","tid":1721421,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:55:46.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e3c9cd5c03ed9e5357b24267826b053facefa575","tid":1721421,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:56:07.000Z","msg":"Thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d776373888d6ddaeb5c28c4c4b90a25bcbb81b","tid":1721421,"uid":39503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:57:26.000Z","msg":"真唔真，唔好氹我哋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"964410c270313c0d640566334b056884859a41d1","tid":1721421,"uid":61769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:57:47.000Z","msg":"Go"